{
  "stem": "151.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that night we were sitting on top of the coal of course not sleeping, very excited about are we going to find anybody in Budapest or not.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in the middle of the night, we noticed that these big sacks on which these girls were sitting are getting lower and lower and lower.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Towards the morning, we saw that they were sitting really on the floor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We also notice that some Russian soldiers were on the outside of the train walking through the train.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We didn't know what they were doing, but in the morning we found out that they were looting these sacks that these girls had.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They cut a window open on the sack and removed everything that was in it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "These girls next morning had nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was sort of bittersweet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I mean, we really didn't mean to be mean, but they were not very nice.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We arrived early in the morning and at the railroad station there were some of the Jews who were in hiding in Budapest waiting for these trains.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They organized and they were waiting every train that came into Budapest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Had nothing to do with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not at that time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At least, we didn't have anything to do with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so these were individuals--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later in Czechoslovakia UNRRA was very active.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what happened in Hungary because we weren't there too long.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I recognized one of the boys from my hometown.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he immediately recognized me and embraced and he was happy to see somebody from his hometown coming home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he took us into the school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the walls of the school were covered with paper and alphabetically everybody signed in.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
